metadata.name: Arcade Weekend
metadata.description:
Collaboration between
Stephanie Priscilla and Annicelric

This collaboration is influenced by our love and nostalgia for 80s/90s
games and anime. A lot of which inspires both our art styles and love for
drawing. This drawing also symbolizes a friendship, one of which we have
grown throughout the years connecting with each-other through art and social media.

The owner of this piece will receive a signed A3 framed poster.

Thank you!
